quran[11]{c,v,t}:
  7,1,"Alif-lam-meem-sad"
  7,2,"Kitabun onzila ilayka falayakun fee sadrika harajun minhu litunthirabihi wathikra lilmu/mineen"
  7,3,"IttabiAAoo ma onzila ilaykum minrabbikum wala tattabiAAoo min doonihi awliyaaqaleelan ma tathakkaroon"
  7,4,"Wakam min qaryatin ahlaknahafajaaha ba/suna bayatan aw hum qa-iloon"
  7,5,"Fama kana daAAwahum ithjaahum ba/suna illa an qaloo innakunna thalimeen"
  7,6,"Falanas-alanna allatheena orsilailayhim walanas-alanna almursaleen"
  7,7,"Falanaqussanna AAalayhim biAAilmin wamakunna gha-ibeen"
  7,8,"Walwaznu yawma-ithini alhaqqufaman thaqulat mawazeenuhu faola-ika humu almuflihoon"
  7,9,"Waman khaffat mawazeenuhu faola-ikaallatheena khasiroo anfusahum bima kanoo bi-ayatinayathlimoon"
  7,10,"Walaqad makkannakum fee al-ardiwajaAAalna lakum feeha maAAayisha qaleelan matashkuroon"
  7,11,"Walaqad khalaqnakum thumma sawwarnakumthumma qulna lilmala-ikati osjudoo li-adamafasajadoo illa ibleesa lam yakun mina assajideen"
